WEBVTT

00:00.600 --> 00:03.602
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:03.604 --> 00:05.604
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:05.606 --> 00:07.539
BLAKE WAS P.O.'ed

00:07.541 --> 00:09.708
HEY...

00:09.710 --> 00:12.211
IS THAT CHILD STAR
CHUGGY SIMPLE?

00:12.213 --> 00:13.312
IT SURE IS.

00:13.314 --> 00:14.680
WOW.

00:14.682 --> 00:17.016
WHY DID HE REFER TO YOU
AS "DR. BETH," NURSE BETH?

00:17.018 --> 00:21.553
WELL, DO YOU WANT THE SHORT
VERSION OR THE LONG VERSION?

00:21.555 --> 00:23.055
ACTUALLY, I ONLY HAVE TIME
FOR THE SHORT VERSION.

00:23.057 --> 00:24.823
THEN I GUESS I'LL START
WAY BACK AT THE BEGINNING.

00:24.825 --> 00:26.625
IT WAS FOUR YEARS AGO.

00:26.627 --> 00:28.060
THERE'S A NEW NURSE
STARTING TODAY.

00:28.062 --> 00:29.795
SY ASSIGNED ME
TO SEXUALLY HARASS HER,

00:29.797 --> 00:31.130
LIKE I DON'T HAVE ENOUGH
TO DO.

00:31.132 --> 00:32.698
I KNOW -- IT'S LIKE,
DO THEY WANT US

00:32.700 --> 00:34.133
TO CARE
FOR OUR PATIENTS

00:34.135 --> 00:37.202
OR SPEND ALL DAY
SEXUALLY HARASSING THE NURSES?

00:41.207 --> 00:42.608
Sal: <i> ATTENTION, NURSES.</i>

00:42.610 --> 00:44.910
<i>8:00 A.M. SHIFT BEGINS</i>
<i>IN ONE MINUTE.</i>

00:44.912 --> 00:47.679
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK,
NURSE BETH? YOU READY?

00:47.681 --> 00:49.181
I'M SO NERVOUS, NURSE JANET.

00:49.183 --> 00:52.017
OH, WELL, EVERYONE'S NERVOUS
THEIR FIRST TIME UPSTAIRS.

00:52.019 --> 00:54.453
JUST KEEP YOUR EARS OPEN,
YOUR MOUTH CLOSED,

00:54.455 --> 00:55.888
AND YOUR EYES...

00:55.890 --> 00:59.191
WELL, JUST DO WHAT YOU NORMALLY
DO WITH YOUR EYES.

01:00.093 --> 01:00.959
Woman: EVERYBODY!

01:00.961 --> 01:03.462
NURSE DORI.
IT'S DORI!

01:03.464 --> 01:05.531
8:00 A.M., NURSES.
LET'S GO.

01:05.533 --> 01:07.266
YES, NURSE DORI, MA'AM.

01:07.268 --> 01:08.367
YES, MA'AM.

01:08.369 --> 01:10.569
YOU!
COME WITH ME, ROOKIE.

01:11.371 --> 01:15.707
♪♪

01:21.881 --> 01:24.183
THIS IS
WHERE IT ALL HAPPENS --

01:24.185 --> 01:27.052
LIFE, DEATH,
AND EVERYTHING IN BETWEEN.

01:27.054 --> 01:28.454
YOU MEAN LIKE
SOME SORT OF LIMINAL ZONE

01:28.456 --> 01:29.922
BETWEEN LIFE AND DEATH?

01:29.924 --> 01:31.190
NO.

01:31.192 --> 01:32.191
DOCTORS.

01:32.193 --> 01:34.093
OH, YEAH.

01:34.095 --> 01:35.594
WATCH OUT FOR THEM.

01:35.596 --> 01:37.129
THIS IS YOUR STATION.
UH-HUH.

01:37.131 --> 01:38.931
DON'T OVERDO IT
ON THE PERFUME.

01:38.933 --> 01:40.999
ALWAYS KEEP
A NEEDLE AND THREAD CLOSE,

01:41.001 --> 01:43.102
AND BUY YOURSELF
A NICE PUSH-UP BRA.

01:43.104 --> 01:44.036
MM-HMM.

01:44.038 --> 01:45.771
DOCTORS THINK
THEY NEED A NURSE,

01:45.773 --> 01:47.539
BUT WHAT THEY REALLY NEED
IS SOMETHING BETWEEN A MOTHER

01:47.541 --> 01:48.907
AND A WAIST-HIGH HOOKER
WITH NO TEETH

01:48.909 --> 01:50.909
WHO HAS HANDLEBARS
FOR EARS.

01:50.911 --> 01:53.412
ALSO, BUY YOURSELF
SOME NICE EAR HANDLEBARS.

01:53.414 --> 01:55.114
THANKS, DORI.

01:55.116 --> 01:56.515
<i>NURSE</i> DORI.

01:56.517 --> 01:57.883
NURSE DORI.

01:57.885 --> 02:00.219
HEY, NURSE BETH.
BLAKE DOWNS, M.D.

02:00.221 --> 02:03.722
I'M THE DOCTOR WHO'S BEEN
ASSIGNED TO SEXUALLY HARASS YOU.

02:03.724 --> 02:06.058
OKAY.
THE CONTENT WILL BE SEXUAL,
OF COURSE.

02:06.060 --> 02:08.360
YOU UNDERSTAND --
IT'S JUST THE POWER DYNAMIC

02:08.362 --> 02:09.428
WE'RE ENFORCING.

02:09.430 --> 02:11.130
SO, LET'S BEGIN.
[ BEEPING ]

02:11.132 --> 02:12.197
OH, DAMN IT.
MM.

02:12.199 --> 02:13.298
GOT TO PUT A PIN IN THIS.

02:13.300 --> 02:15.734
UM, WHAT'S YOUR EARLY AFTERNOON
LOOKING LIKE?

02:15.736 --> 02:19.705
NURSE, PATIENT IN ROOM 314
SOILED HIMSELF.

02:19.707 --> 02:23.609
NURSE!
DOCTOR IN 314 SOILED HIMSELF.

02:24.777 --> 02:26.979
NURSE!
I SOILED MYSELF.

02:26.981 --> 02:28.647
-RIGHT DOWN HERE.
-I SOILED MYSELF.

02:28.649 --> 02:31.617
-I DID IT.
-I DID IT AGAIN.
-I DID IT AGAIN.

02:31.619 --> 02:33.452
[ ALL TALKING AT ONCE ]

02:33.454 --> 02:35.854
Man: I DID IT.

02:35.856 --> 02:37.156
THE DOCTORS ARE SO MEAN.

02:37.158 --> 02:39.124
THEY DON'T EVEN
WIPE THEMSELVES.

02:39.126 --> 02:40.893
AND I'M ON MY FEET
ALL DAY,

02:40.895 --> 02:42.394
EXCEPT WHEN I'M ON MY HANDS,

02:42.396 --> 02:45.197
BECAUSE SOMETIMES THEY MAKE ME
WALK AROUND ON MY HANDS.

02:45.199 --> 02:46.565
OH, YOU'LL GET USED TO IT.

02:46.567 --> 02:48.600
IT'S ALL ABOUT
WEIGHT DISTRIBUTION.

02:48.602 --> 02:49.768
I DON'T THINK
I CAN DO THIS.

02:49.770 --> 02:51.803
OH, NO.
ARE YOU GIVING UP ALREADY?

02:51.805 --> 02:53.438
THAT'S A RECORD.

02:53.440 --> 02:55.607
I SHOULD CALL <i> THE GUINNESS BOOK</i>
<i>OF WORLD RECORDS.</i>

02:55.609 --> 02:58.644
[ CRYING ]

03:00.780 --> 03:03.582
YOU MUST BE BETH.

03:03.584 --> 03:05.317
I'M FLOSSIE.

03:05.319 --> 03:07.252
FOLKS AROUND HERE CALL ME

03:07.254 --> 03:10.322
"THAT OLD NURSE
WHO'S DYING OF EMPHYSEMA."

03:11.424 --> 03:12.858
TOUGH FIRST DAY?

03:12.860 --> 03:15.394
NURSE DORI HATES ME.

03:15.396 --> 03:18.163
MIGHT BE SHE SEES SOMETHING
IN YOU LIKE I DO.

03:19.165 --> 03:22.501
AND SHE'S AFRAID
OF HER OWN STANDING.

03:22.503 --> 03:24.536
YOU JUST PAY HER NO MIND.

03:24.538 --> 03:25.771
THANKS, FLOSSIE.

03:25.773 --> 03:27.739
YOU SURE DO HAVE
A WHITE MAN'S IDEA

03:27.741 --> 03:29.975
OF AN AFRICAN-AMERICAN WAY
ABOUT YOU.

03:29.977 --> 03:32.878
I DON'T HAVE
A LOT OF FRIENDS AROUND HERE.

03:32.880 --> 03:36.415
NURSE JANET SEEMS NICE,
BUT SHE'S PROBABLY A DUMB SLUT.

03:36.417 --> 03:37.916
WELL, YOU JUST COME TO ME

03:37.918 --> 03:40.786
ANY TIME YOU NEED MOTHERIN',
DARLIN'.

03:40.788 --> 03:43.755
I'M HERE
AND I AIN'T GOING NOWHERE.

03:43.757 --> 03:46.558
I LOVE YOU, FLOSSIE.

03:46.560 --> 03:47.859
[ COUGHING ]

03:47.861 --> 03:51.230
OH, NO, I'M LATE FOR SURGERY!
I GOT TO GO!

03:51.232 --> 03:54.733
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

03:57.370 --> 03:59.938
HM, HOW NICE OF YOU TO JOIN US,
NURSE BETH.

03:59.940 --> 04:01.273
YEAH, I'LL SAY.

04:01.275 --> 04:02.874
YOU LOOK PRETTY HOT
IN SURGICAL SCRUBS.

04:02.876 --> 04:04.409
UH, OWEN. SORRY, MAN.

04:04.411 --> 04:06.578
BUT IF IT'S NOT <i> ME</i>
SEXUALLY HARASSING NURSE BETH,

04:06.580 --> 04:08.146
SY'S GONNA BE
ALL OVER MY ASS.

04:08.148 --> 04:09.948
OH, RIGHT. I FORGOT.
APOLOGIES.

04:09.950 --> 04:12.150
IS IT OKAY IF I TELL YOU
ABOUT A STRIP CLUB

04:12.152 --> 04:14.253
THAT ME AND MY BOYS
HIT THE OTHER NIGHT?

04:14.255 --> 04:16.954
AS LONG AS IT DOESN'T DIRECTLY
REFERENCE NURSE BETH,

04:16.957 --> 04:18.357
WE SHOULD BE FINE.

04:18.358 --> 04:19.658
GREAT.

04:19.660 --> 04:22.327
BECAUSE THIS PLACE HAD IT ALL --
CHAIRS, BATHROOMS, AN ATM.

04:22.329 --> 04:24.229
HEY, IS THAT CHILD STAR
CHUGGY SIMPLE?

04:24.231 --> 04:26.832
THEY EVEN HAD A PAY PHONE
RIGHT BY THE CASH REGISTER.

04:26.834 --> 04:28.433
UH, DR. MAESTRO,
YOU'RE ABOUT TO --

04:28.435 --> 04:30.068
BY THE WAY,
THEY HAD A CASH REGISTER --

04:30.070 --> 04:31.436
DR. MAESTRO!
WHAT?

04:31.438 --> 04:33.972
YOU'RE ABOUT TO HIT CHUGGY'S
SUBCLAVIAN ARTERY.

04:33.974 --> 04:35.474
IF YOU CUT THAT, HE'LL DIE.

04:35.476 --> 04:37.643
OH, MY GOD, YOU'RE RIGHT.

04:37.645 --> 04:39.177
GOOD THING SY ISN'T HERE.

04:39.179 --> 04:41.647
BUT I AM HERE.

04:41.649 --> 04:43.515
I'M SO IMPRESSED,
NURSE BETH.

04:43.517 --> 04:44.716
YOU ARE?
YEAH.

04:44.718 --> 04:46.351
THIS CROISSANT
IS THREE DAYS OLD,

04:46.353 --> 04:49.388
AND YET IT TASTES LIKE A
BUTTERY ANGEL PEED IN MY MOUTH.

04:49.390 --> 04:52.090
AND ALSO, I'M IMPRESSED
WITH YOUR REALLY QUICK THINKING.

04:52.092 --> 04:54.926
YOU KNOW WHAT,
YOU'RE NO LONGER A NURSE.

04:54.928 --> 04:57.296
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
I AM SO PROUD TO INTRODUCE

04:57.298 --> 04:59.398
CHILDRENS HOSPITAL'S
NEWEST DOCTOR,

04:59.400 --> 05:00.565
DR. BETH!

05:00.567 --> 05:02.200
WHAT?
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

05:02.202 --> 05:05.504
YOU JUST WAVE YOUR HANDS, AND
ALL OF A SUDDEN, SHE'S A DOCTOR?

05:05.506 --> 05:06.738
YES.

05:06.740 --> 05:08.340
OKAY, COOL.
I GUESS YOU'RE ONE OF US.

05:08.342 --> 05:09.675
OH.
GOOD JOB.

05:09.677 --> 05:11.143
WAIT, STOP EVERYTHING!

05:11.145 --> 05:13.912
IF ANYONE IS GONNA BECOME
A DOCTOR, IT'S ME.

05:13.914 --> 05:17.149
GUARDS, COULD YOU REMOVE
THIS NURSE FROM THE O.R.?

05:17.151 --> 05:19.818
GUARDS?

05:19.820 --> 05:21.320
OH, NO!

05:21.322 --> 05:23.789
SCALPEL.

05:25.558 --> 05:28.393
ALL RIGHT.
LET'S DO THIS.

05:30.663 --> 05:32.097
SO, WHERE WILL YOU LIVE NOW?

05:32.099 --> 05:35.167
THEY'RE GIVING ME A SUITE
IN THE DOCTOR'S PENTHOUSE.

05:35.169 --> 05:36.335
[ GASPS ]

05:36.337 --> 05:37.836
I KNOW!
WHAT?

05:37.838 --> 05:39.871
LADIES, GET BACK TO WORK.

05:39.873 --> 05:43.375
ACTUALLY,
IT'S OKAY, GIRLS.

05:43.377 --> 05:45.210
YOU CAN STAY.

05:46.813 --> 05:49.581
DOCTOR'S ORDERS.

05:54.821 --> 05:56.588
[ COUGHS ]

05:56.590 --> 05:58.156
SO, WHAT DO YOU GUYS THINK?

05:58.158 --> 05:59.691
SHOULD I JUST GO AHEAD
AND SPRING FOR THE TESLA, OR...

05:59.693 --> 06:02.427
HEY. DR. BETH.

06:02.429 --> 06:05.831
I GOT SOMEONE HERE
WHO WANTS TO SAY HELLO.

06:05.833 --> 06:06.998
CHUGGY SIMPLE.

06:07.000 --> 06:08.567
YOU SAVED MY LIFE.

06:08.569 --> 06:10.202
GIVE ME A CHUGGY HUGGY!

06:10.204 --> 06:12.704
I'M HAVING ANOTHER PROCEDURE
TOMORROW,

06:12.706 --> 06:15.807
AND I REQUESTED
THAT YOU PERFORM THE SURGERY.

06:15.809 --> 06:18.276
I AM HONORED, CHUGGY.
I --

06:18.278 --> 06:22.280
HEY, DR. BETH,
WE GOT YOU ONE MORE GIFT.

06:22.282 --> 06:25.917
♪♪

06:31.891 --> 06:34.659
IT'S A DOCTOR'S COAT.

06:34.661 --> 06:36.228
WOW.

06:38.865 --> 06:41.533
YOU LOOK LOVELY,
DR. BETH.

06:41.535 --> 06:44.736
EXCUSE ME, NURSE,
WHO SAID YOU COULD TALK TO ME?

06:44.738 --> 06:45.971
[ LAUGHS ]

06:45.973 --> 06:48.206
WALK ON YOUR HANDS.

06:48.208 --> 06:51.410
NOW!

06:57.016 --> 06:59.951
THANK YOU.

07:03.623 --> 07:05.724
UGH.

07:05.726 --> 07:07.559
[ GRUNTS ]

07:10.530 --> 07:15.200
NURSE DORI, I DON'T LIKE
THE LOOK ON YOUR FACE.

07:15.202 --> 07:17.135
BETH'S GONNA BE RELYING
ON A NURSE

07:17.137 --> 07:19.104
TO HAND HER
THE CORRECT INSTRUMENTS

07:19.106 --> 07:20.672
AT CHUGGY'S SURGERY
TOMORROW.

07:20.674 --> 07:24.142
BUT I'M NOT GONNA HAND HER
THE CORRECT INSTRUMENTS.

07:24.144 --> 07:27.679
I'M GONNA HAND HER INSTRUMENTS
THAT ARE NOT CORRECT.

07:27.681 --> 07:30.115
THE INCORRECT ONES.

07:30.117 --> 07:32.517
HATE IS LIKE A FIRE,
HONEY.

07:35.421 --> 07:38.457
THEN LET IT BURN.

07:40.326 --> 07:43.028
[ COUGHS ]

07:44.030 --> 07:47.666
OH, MEANWHILE, I'M DYING.

07:47.668 --> 07:51.203
♪♪

07:53.039 --> 07:54.973
DON'T GO IN THERE, GIRL.

07:54.975 --> 07:57.108
[ COUGHING ]

07:58.845 --> 08:01.012
IF YOU'RE NOT GONNA
SPIT IT OUT,

08:01.014 --> 08:03.315
THEN GET OUT OF MY WAY,
NURSE.

08:03.317 --> 08:05.116
DOR-- DORI...

08:05.118 --> 08:06.885
SETTING YOU UP...

08:06.887 --> 08:09.788
[ COUGHS ]

08:09.790 --> 08:11.323
AH.

08:11.325 --> 08:13.258
ANYWAY.

08:13.260 --> 08:16.528
Man: WE'RE READY
FOR YOUR SURGERY, DR. BETH.

08:20.833 --> 08:23.134
I CAN TAKE OVER,
NURSE JANET.

08:23.136 --> 08:24.636
YES, MA'AM.

08:24.638 --> 08:28.206
IF THE NURSES ARE DONE CHATTING,
MAYBE WE COULD BEGIN?

08:28.208 --> 08:29.708
I'M SORRY, DR. BETH.

08:29.710 --> 08:32.177
SCALPEL.

08:42.054 --> 08:44.589
RETRACTOR.

08:48.294 --> 08:50.762
OH, DOCTOR,
HE'S BLEEDING OUT.

08:50.764 --> 08:52.063
GAUZE! GAUZE!

08:52.065 --> 08:56.034
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

08:56.036 --> 08:58.670
HE'S CRASHING.
DEFIBRILLATOR!

08:58.672 --> 09:00.205
DEFIBRILLATOR!

09:03.342 --> 09:05.210
CLEAR!

09:05.212 --> 09:08.346
[ MONITOR BEEPING RAPIDLY ]

09:08.348 --> 09:11.716
CLEAR!

09:11.718 --> 09:13.618
[ MONITOR BEEPING RAPIDLY ]

09:13.620 --> 09:16.321
[ FLATLINE ]

09:18.190 --> 09:22.093
DR. BETH, YOUR ONLY JOB
WAS TO KEEP CHUGGY ALIVE.

09:22.095 --> 09:23.895
YOU DID THE OPPOSITE.

09:23.897 --> 09:24.996
I WAS W--

09:24.998 --> 09:27.165
I WAS WR--
WRONG ABOUT YOU.

09:27.167 --> 09:30.502
DR. BETH,
I AM DEMOTING YOU DOWN TO NURSE.

09:30.504 --> 09:32.737
HAND OVER
YOUR DOCTOR'S COAT.

09:32.739 --> 09:36.141
♪♪

09:38.244 --> 09:40.946
FLOSSIE, I AM SO SORRY!

09:40.948 --> 09:44.849
I HAVE BEEN A JERK
TO EVERYBODY!

09:44.851 --> 09:47.452
FLOSSIE? FLOSSIE?

09:47.454 --> 09:49.054
SHE'S GONE.
GONE?

09:49.056 --> 09:51.156
BUT I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
SHE WAS SICK.

09:51.158 --> 09:52.457
NO ONE DID.

09:52.459 --> 09:55.260
SHE WAS PROBABLY TOO PROUD
TO SHOW IT.

09:55.262 --> 09:56.761
I WAS AWFUL TO HER.

09:56.763 --> 09:58.330
I WAS PRETTY COOL.

09:58.332 --> 10:01.733
SHE ALWAYS SAW THE BEST
IN PEOPLE.

10:01.735 --> 10:05.904
AND NOW I DO TOO.

10:05.906 --> 10:09.074
I'M SORRY I WAS SUCH A...

10:09.076 --> 10:10.208
NURSE.

10:10.210 --> 10:14.012
I'M SORRY
I WAS SUCH A DOCTOR.

10:14.014 --> 10:15.180
FRIENDS?

10:15.182 --> 10:17.015
YEAH. FRIENDS.

10:17.017 --> 10:18.450
COME HERE.

10:18.684 --> 10:23.254
AND THAT'S WHY, FOR THAT
ONE DAY, I WAS CALLED DR. BETH.

10:23.256 --> 10:24.556
HEY, WHERE'D CAT GO?

10:24.558 --> 10:26.625
OH, SHE LEFT
A LONG TIME AGO,

10:26.627 --> 10:29.828
RIGHT AROUND THE EAR HANDLEBARS
PART, I THINK.

10:29.830 --> 10:31.162
HEY, THAT REMINDS ME.

10:31.164 --> 10:33.398
I NEED TO GET
NEW EAR HANDLEBARS.

10:33.400 --> 10:35.367
MY -- MY GRIPS ARE WORN.

10:38.604 --> 10:41.706
♪♪

10:44.210 --> 10:46.745
♪ IT SEEMS SO CLEAR ♪

10:46.747 --> 10:48.413
♪ WHEN I LOOK BACK ♪

10:48.415 --> 10:50.949
♪ 20/20
AND ALL THAT OTHER CRAP ♪

10:50.951 --> 10:54.319
♪ EVERY NEW ROOF
HAS A RISK OF A NEW COLLAPSE ♪

10:54.321 --> 10:57.789
♪ EVERY NEW DOLLAR
IS A RISK OF A NEW TAX ♪

10:57.791 --> 11:00.925
♪ RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOUR FACE,
BUT YOU CAN'T SEE ♪

11:00.927 --> 11:04.429
♪ RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOUR FACE,
BUT YOU CAN'T SEE ♪

11:04.431 --> 11:08.700
♪ RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOUR FACE,
